Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.45,0:00:10.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふたりがきっと　出会えるような　魔法をかけて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施展了倆人一定會相遇的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,両手をそっと　重ねてほら　ほほえむから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄的合起雙手 你看 在微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとの気持ち　気付かないふりして
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心情 卻當作沒有察覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然ふたり　恋に落ちたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然 倆人陷入了愛河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.70,0:01:08.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だきしめたいのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想擁抱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.10,0:01:22.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.50,0:01:30.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.43,0:01:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.87,0:01:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是討厭的天氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.24,0:01:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不該聽那個故事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.98,0:01:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是個發生在似乎即將下雨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.68,0:01:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悶熱陰天的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.48,0:01:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在這天遭到殺害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.19,0:01:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她和深愛的男人\N幽會時的暗號遭到利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.16,0:01:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慘遭因嫉妒而發狂的妻子殺害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.33,0:01:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人的怨念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.96,0:02:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今仍徘徊在那間公寓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.06,0:02:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在悶熱的陰天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.37,0:02:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就會發出那個暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.10,0:02:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人以前所用的幽會暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.94,0:02:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將房間的電燈關了又開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.21,0:02:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關了又開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.14,0:02:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後在那裡等待著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.28,0:02:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等待著新的犧牲者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.92,0:02:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#11  ちぃ，確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.70,0:02:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.97,0:02:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.07,0:02:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.34,0:02:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.17,0:02:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是指這間公寓嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.74,0:02:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.81,0:02:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.28,0:02:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將房間的電燈開了又關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.95,0:02:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是有婦之夫和愛人幽會的暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.89,0:03:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.82,0:03:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她像往常一般進了房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.96,0:03:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡等待著她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.43,0:03:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻是手持菜刀的男人的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.60,0:03:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是個發生在似乎即將下雨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.70,0:03:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悶熱陰天的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.84,0:03:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在這天遭到殺害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.81,0:03:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人為了找男人求救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.55,0:03:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拼命朝門口爬去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.15,0:03:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻在門前力氣用盡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.72,0:03:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人也沒有來接她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.92,0:03:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.09,0:03:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個女人也被男人背叛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.09,0:03:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽會時的暗號遭到利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.76,0:03:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慘遭妻子殺害的女人怨念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.63,0:03:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今仍徘徊在那間公寓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.57,0:03:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在跟她遇害當天\N同樣的悶熱陰天裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.57,0:03:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就會發出那個暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.38,0:03:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人以前所用的幽會暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.68,0:03:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將房間的電燈關了又開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.91,0:04:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關了又開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.68,0:04:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後在那裡等待著新的犧牲者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.39,0:04:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在G公寓的104號房裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.76,0:04:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個網站以討論謠傳為主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.23,0:04:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方即使沒有螢幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.63,0:04:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦也會用簡單易懂的方式\N唸給你聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.30,0:04:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.84,0:04:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己來問我網路的事的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.21,0:04:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我去一下廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.71,0:04:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟在稔他家聽到的故事一模一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.75,0:04:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.15,0:04:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算今天是陰天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.05,0:04:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算一樓的空房間燈亮著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.92,0:04:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.76,0:04:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去澡堂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.19,0:04:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.09,0:04:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.69,0:04:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.40,0:04:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.73,0:04:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼悶熱的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.33,0:04:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在玩什麼奇怪的遊戲嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.00,0:04:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要打開囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.41,0:04:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，這個人好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.47,0:05:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.14,0:05:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,104號房的鬼故事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.31,0:05:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個網站我也看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.68,0:05:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只是常聽到的恐怖故事而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.35,0:05:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你也是這麼想的對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.28,0:05:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我剛剛看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.45,0:05:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一樓角落的房間電燈在閃爍著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.29,0:05:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且故事裡提到的G公寓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.26,0:05:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也叫作“GAB城崎”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.79,0:05:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想太多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.96,0:05:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且一樓角落的房間又沒人住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.07,0:05:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有在閃爍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.24,0:05:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.37,0:05:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.87,0:05:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你膽子這麼小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.28,0:05:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.41,0:05:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天你睡這裡好不好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.11,0:05:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要在隔壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.48,0:05:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是男生的房間睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.22,0:05:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.92,0:05:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就好，今天就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.65,0:05:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會對你做什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.92,0:05:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做了還得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.77,0:05:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都已經天亮了，竟然還睡不著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.37,0:06:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.68,0:06:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.84,0:06:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.41,0:06:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.88,0:06:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.66,0:06:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.91,0:06:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.38,0:06:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聲音不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.55,0:06:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳突然是怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.62,0:06:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.46,0:06:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.34,0:07:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.01,0:07:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底看到了什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.78,0:07:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，你怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.15,0:07:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體不舒服嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.49,0:07:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.82,0:07:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.09,0:07:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好怕的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.09,0:07:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那我要出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.13,0:07:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以出去亂跑喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.26,0:07:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這果然就是那個鬼故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.60,0:07:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以靠近那個房間喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.70,0:07:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去問問看管理員好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.17,0:07:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過要怎麼開口問啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道要問她\N“這間公寓被詛咒了嗎？”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.05,0:07:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來就已經遲交房租了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.81,0:07:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說這個感覺就像是故意在找麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.35,0:07:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和，那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.59,0:07:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近天氣真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.75,0:07:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雲層很厚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.86,0:08:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，完全沒什麼奇怪的現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.79,0:08:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.69,0:08:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.40,0:08:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.41,0:08:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道真是我想太多了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.08,0:08:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.64,0:08:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是身邊老是發生那種事\N誰還受得了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.08,0:08:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是公寓名稱裡有個“G”字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.02,0:08:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是GonzaIez\N或是GaI&Do之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.62,0:08:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,況且那個故事巧合實在太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.09,0:08:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼門打開\N就有女人拿著菜刀站著…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.30,0:08:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.77,0:08:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧？學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.60,0:08:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.44,0:08:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，嚇到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.61,0:08:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.97,0:08:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟妳說這種奇怪的故事\N我才覺得不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼詛咒報應之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.28,0:09:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己都這個年紀了\N總覺得很丟臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.25,0:09:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.42,0:09:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會怕黑色的動物之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑色的？為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.62,0:09:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如說烏鴉、黑貓\N還有蝙蝠之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.56,0:09:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不但不吉利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.83,0:09:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還覺得有點恐怖不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.70,0:09:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.86,0:09:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定只是裝作毫不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.27,0:09:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實心裡怕得要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.63,0:09:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你根本不需要在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.27,0:09:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是嚇了一跳而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.84,0:09:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不用那麼擔心啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.68,0:09:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次去看電影的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.05,0:09:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒跟學長說就先回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.72,0:09:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.02,0:09:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.56,0:09:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.46,0:09:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想說妳可能是有急事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.26,0:09:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不用放在心上啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.06,0:09:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.06,0:09:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你方便的話，下次再一起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.43,0:09:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂意之至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.41,0:09:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請振作點，學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.41,0:10:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.65,0:10:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算被嚇到也要有個程度吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.75,0:10:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道什麼鬼不鬼故事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.69,0:10:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我背一個男人回家\N你好歹也要替我想想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.62,0:10:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.49,0:10:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.59,0:10:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我剛才會暈倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.33,0:10:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟鬼故事沒什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.37,0:10:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,況且你仔細想想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.37,0:10:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這棟公寓根本沒有104號房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.50,0:10:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為一樓只有三個房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.51,0:10:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.54,0:10:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從大門向左邊算去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.11,0:10:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是管理員住的101號房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.01,0:10:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後右邊有兩間房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.88,0:10:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣算來，那104號房在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.78,0:10:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懂了的話，就忘了那個故事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.52,0:10:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.79,0:10:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還會痛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.03,0:10:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，不會痛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.87,0:11:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，你害怕那個房間嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.67,0:11:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？沒有，那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.64,0:11:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ去確認看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.27,0:11:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.38,0:11:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這棟公寓根本沒有104號房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.95,0:11:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.55,0:11:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.32,0:11:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.79,0:11:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有104號房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.22,0:11:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個故事根本就不成立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.22,0:11:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一樓有三個房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.13,0:11:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日比谷住的101號室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.66,0:11:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下兩間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.43,0:11:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,102
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.53,0:11:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有103
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.64,0:11:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然只是空房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.85,0:11:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是個大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.96,0:11:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停電了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.29,0:11:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打雷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.59,0:11:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來很近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.90,0:12:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.24,0:12:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.77,0:12:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.25,0:12:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.52,0:12:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.52,0:12:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.03,0:12:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.06,0:12:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.24,0:12:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.25,0:12:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是夢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.11,0:12:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.75,0:12:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.92,0:12:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經快要中午了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.22,0:12:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要睡到什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.69,0:13:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也提起精神到補習班去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.59,0:13:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇，已經這麼晚了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.56,0:13:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.56,0:13:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你萬事如意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.59,0:13:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，對不起把妳吵醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.70,0:13:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.13,0:13:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹要去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.40,0:13:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡？我要去補習班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.27,0:13:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.54,0:13:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,104號房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.54,0:13:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，請用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.54,0:13:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香草的可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.81,0:13:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，這裡是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.82,0:13:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.08,0:13:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是學長你說如果方便的話\N下次再一起出來玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.32,0:13:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才帶我來的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.39,0:13:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.12,0:13:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太棒了，天氣這麼好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.39,0:13:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想坐那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個小船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.83,0:13:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾玩這個也不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.23,0:13:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧，我很喜歡玩這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.77,0:13:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從樹木之間射出的陽光真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.91,0:13:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我想起了老家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.68,0:13:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再過去還有更美的地方喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.81,0:14:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是一棟古老的公寓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從一樓的窗戶可以看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.35,0:14:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電燈在閃爍著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.50,0:14:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.60,0:14:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.27,0:14:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.64,0:14:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡發呆很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.57,0:14:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.54,0:14:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最近怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.08,0:14:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.38,0:14:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？沒有，沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.01,0:14:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.42,0:14:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對，你沒必要跟我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.89,0:14:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我只是補習班的老師而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.63,0:14:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去喝一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.43,0:14:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走嘛，走嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.60,0:14:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直有事想跟本須和說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.67,0:14:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老…老師，這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.94,0:14:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人單獨去不太好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.51,0:14:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帶你去一間很棒的店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.68,0:15:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.05,0:15:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想說\N一定要帶本須和來一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.52,0:15:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老…老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.26,0:15:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師，不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.83,0:15:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不行？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.86,0:15:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原…原來是夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.13,0:15:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.27,0:15:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說夢話說得還真大聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.70,0:15:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去洗把臉再回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.70,0:15:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.78,0:15:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可是三樓耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.38,0:15:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.68,0:15:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.81,0:15:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那之後我根本睡不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.25,0:15:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.79,0:15:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管睡著或醒著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.79,0:15:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腦裡都一直想著104號房的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.19,0:15:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你，新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.36,0:15:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪我一起睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.19,0:15:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來病得不輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.13,0:15:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.53,0:15:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.43,0:15:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就一起去驅鬼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.27,0:15:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.73,0:16:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要來我家？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.80,0:16:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是說\N是我造成本須和精神衰竭的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.54,0:16:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，不是那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.44,0:16:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果弄清楚那個故事的來源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.04,0:16:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想說應該可以\N讓這傢伙安心一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.68,0:16:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算想找來源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.91,0:16:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,網路上流傳的鬼故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.35,0:16:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎都是不可信的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.32,0:16:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,104號房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.39,0:16:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是104號房？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.32,0:16:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.39,0:16:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界上的確存在著\N無數的謎團和怪事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.16,0:16:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過大部分都是自己看錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.40,0:16:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屬於自然現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.43,0:16:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不過我的確聽到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.11,0:16:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在地板上爬的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.97,0:16:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有流出來的黑血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.18,0:16:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我親眼看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.88,0:16:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你所說的“親眼看到”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.31,0:16:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時候是最不可信的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.22,0:16:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人在潛意識中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.95,0:16:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很容易就能看到\N自己想看或是想相信的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.42,0:16:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.29,0:16:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我真的看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.39,0:16:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那間不應該有的104號房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.43,0:17:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的存在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.40,0:17:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.23,0:17:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個鬼故事\N說的果然就是GAB城崎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.57,0:17:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.41,0:17:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去GAB城崎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.91,0:17:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣看來，似乎還真有那種氣氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.78,0:17:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要那種氣氛啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.88,0:17:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼偏偏又是這種天氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.72,0:17:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是靈異現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.29,0:17:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不正是調查的好時機嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.09,0:17:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.36,0:17:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.56,0:17:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.86,0:17:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳沒事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.66,0:17:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.06,0:17:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會有事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.76,0:17:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有問題的是哪一間？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.87,0:17:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從大門看去\N左邊是管理員住的101號房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.14,0:17:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後右邊有兩間空房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.98,0:17:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和看到電燈閃爍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.21,0:17:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是裡面的角落房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.41,0:17:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問一下，那時候本須和是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.15,0:17:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只…只有我一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.25,0:17:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保有看過嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.22,0:17:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.95,0:18:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉也沒看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.59,0:18:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼看錯的可能性越來越…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.00,0:18:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.95,0:18:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，怕那個聲音嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就不怕了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.05,0:18:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去確認看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.36,0:18:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這裡守著\N看看有沒有人跑出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.83,0:18:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.16,0:18:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.00,0:18:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是低級的惡作劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.30,0:18:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是被我找到\N我就把你抓起來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.37,0:18:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保少爺好慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.98,0:18:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.48,0:18:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.98,0:19:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.82,0:19:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去上面看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.42,0:19:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.35,0:19:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？等一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.62,0:19:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.69,0:19:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.59,0:19:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.93,0:19:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.96,0:19:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身…身體動不了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.77,0:19:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，不能過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.98,0:19:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快動，快動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.21,0:19:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…ちぃ她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.69,0:19:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.30,0:19:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倉庫？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.53,0:19:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.50,0:19:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為最近東西容易發霉潮濕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.70,0:19:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本想來個大掃除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.97,0:19:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是電燈泡快要壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.87,0:19:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直沒辦法打掃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.97,0:20:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了換燈泡\N我找來了各種東西墊腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.31,0:20:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我還是碰不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.98,0:20:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會叫我來幫忙換
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.02,0:20:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.89,0:20:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是從門下面\N流出的黑色液體…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.39,0:20:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我搬桌子的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.96,0:20:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不小心打翻了水桶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.19,0:20:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我有上去找本須和幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.83,0:20:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你看起來好像很忙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.74,0:20:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電燈泡、桌子、水桶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.77,0:20:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過為什麼會有104號房？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.31,0:20:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來一樓本來有四間房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.38,0:20:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁是103號房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.72,0:20:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我搬來時做了一點改裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.02,0:20:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缺的是102號房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.06,0:20:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.36,0:20:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.83,0:20:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然被搞得團團轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.30,0:20:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是丟臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.56,0:20:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.43,0:20:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不害怕了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.73,0:21:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.40,0:21:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.31,0:21:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.21,0:21:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在營造什麼氣氛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.08,0:21:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.11,0:21:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.58,0:21:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感到最恐怖的就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.08,0:21:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一想到ちぃ可能被附身時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.08,0:21:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才是我最恐怖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.05,0:21:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.09,0:21:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.32,0:21:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事，真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.82,0:21:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸好什麼事都沒發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.53,0:21:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是蔚藍的天空最棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.10,0:21:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.70,0:21:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.94,0:21:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.01,0:21:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.01,0:21:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，還要睡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.65,0:21:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.59,0:21:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又聽見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.82,0:22:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不經意的走在熟悉的街道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.86,0:22:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確會照映在眼簾中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.80,0:22:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在成群結隊前進的人群中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.07,0:22:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那顆遭到淹沒         感到膽怯的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.78,0:22:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raison         d'etre         像那種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.39,0:23:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raison         d'etre         如同那般的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.66,0:23:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡笑、沉沒、漂流\N究竟是為了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.63,0:23:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找著那把鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.47,0:23:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷的在尋找著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.61,0:23:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.94,0:23:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那扇門的鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.33,0:23:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這台DVD播放機是\N可以玩遊戲的優秀機種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.40,0:23:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然也能以高畫質播放各種影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.80,0:23:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹的臉好紅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.50,0:23:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩遊戲吧，玩遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.34,0:23:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.11,0:23:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,車站前的電器行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.14,0:23:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軟體八折大降價
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.81,0:23:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹臉又紅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.48,0:23:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩遊戲，玩遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.85,0:24:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.48,0:24:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五片一套，一萬元日幣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.22,0:24:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，好料的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.48,0:24:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，好料的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.22,0:24:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits  下一回\N「ちぃ，玩遊戲」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.09,0:24:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空姐、護士、已婚婦女…
